Priority: High.\par
Owner: ____________________\par
Target Date: ____________________\par
Status: ____________________\par
Planned Remediation: Add account inventory, periodic review, dormant account handling, and disablement automation.\par
Evidence to Produce: Account inventory, review logs, disablement job output.\par
Notes: ________________________________________________________________\par
\par
