Target Date: ____________________\par
Status: ____________________\par
Planned Remediation: Implement structured audit logging with defined event catalog, identity correlation, and protected retention.\par
Evidence to Produce: Logging standard, sample events, retention configuration.\par
Notes: ________________________________________________________________\par
\par
